==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: It is difficult to retrieve water after (its container) has been knocked over. 

===Pronunciation===
*[[Pinyin]]: fù shuǐ nán shōu

===Proverb===
'''[[覆]][[水]][[难]][[收]]'''

# [[don't cry over spilt milk]].

===Alternate forms===
[[覆水難收]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

